T16D4409:346a-0: @346a ` // rma bya chen mo las gsungs pa'i smon lam dang bden tshig bzhugs /
T16D4409:346a-2: # // sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16D4409:346a-3: rgyal ba rnam gzigs mya ngan 'tshang la gnas //
T16D4409:346a-4: rgyal ba gtsug tor padma dkar po'i drung //
T16D4409:346a-5: thams cad skyob pa s'a la'i drung na gnas //
T16D4409:346a-6: bram ze 'khor ba 'jig ni shir sha'i drung //
T16D4409:346a-7: sangs rgyas gser thub au dum+w'a ra'i drung //
T16D4409:346a-8: 'od srungs n+ya gro dha yi drung na gnas //
T16D4409:346a-9: sh'akya thub mchog khyad par gnas drung du //
T16D4409:346a-10: phyin nas byang chub thob gyur goo ta ma //
T16D4409:346a-11: sangs rgyas rdzu 'phrul chen po de dag la //
T16D4409:346a-12: mngon par dad pa'i lha gang 'khod pa dag / lha rnams de dag yid dga' mgur gyur nas //
T16D4409:346a-13: rtag tu dge zhing zhi bar 'gyur bar byos /
T16D4409:346a-15: // / sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16D4409:346a-16: rkang gnyis khyed cag bde legs shog / rkang bzhi
T16D4409:346a-17: khyed cag bde legs shog / lam du zhugs rnams
T16D4409:346a-18: bde legs shog / phyir 'ong dag kyang bde legs
T16D4409:346a-19: shog / mtshan mo bde legs nyin bde legs //
T16D4409:346a-20: nyi ma'i gung la bde legs shing //
T16D4409:346a-21: khyed cag kun du bde legs shog / de dag
T16D4409:346a-22: sdig par ma gyur cig / nyi ma thams cad
T16D4409:346a-23: dge ba yin // rgyu skra thams cad bzang po yin //
T16D4409:346a-24: sangs rgyas thams cad rdzu 'phrul che //
T16D4409:346a-25: dgra bcom thams cad zag pa zad //
T16D4409:346a-26: bden pa'i tshig 'dis kun du bde legs su gyur
T16D4409:346a-27: cig / rig sngags kyi rgyal mo rma bya chen
